<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>play games • play the game</xh5><p> <i>play games—</i>act cunningly or dishonestly towards a person: Don’t <u>play games</u>, Mona. I know about the theft, and I know that you know about it.</p><p> <i>play the game—</i>observe the rules or conventions: You can’t deny the role that competitiveness plays in raising standards. So you have to <u>play the game</u> if you want to succeed.</p> </entry>
